      "text": "こうして感謝を伝えるのって緊張するなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I still get nervous expressing gratitude like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
